01:20.539 --> 01:21.707
Lizzy?

01:21.707 --> 01:22.958
[Lizzy] Brad?

01:22.958 --> 01:24.460
[eerie breathing]

01:24.460 --> 01:25.586
Brad?

01:25.586 --> 01:28.589
[mysterious music]

01:28.589 --> 01:30.341
♪ ♪

01:30.341 --> 01:32.634
My love, it's Lizzy!

01:32.634 --> 01:33.636
Brad!

01:33.636 --> 01:35.304
[tapping]

01:35.304 --> 01:37.890
♪ ♪

01:37.890 --> 01:40.434
Brad. Brad!

01:40.434 --> 01:42.853
