01:42.853 --> 01:45.606
♪ ♪

01:45.606 --> 01:46.816
Brad!

01:46.816 --> 01:49.276
Is that you?

01:49.276 --> 01:51.320
Is that you?

01:51.320 --> 01:55.074
Brad, is that you?

01:55.074 --> 01:58.077
[voice echoing]

01:58.077 --> 02:02.039
♪ ♪

02:02.623 --> 02:04.083
