02:18.722 --> 02:19.723
Yeah, I am.

02:19.723 --> 02:21.559
Or I was.

02:21.559 --> 02:22.685
Or I'm inconsistent.

02:22.685 --> 02:24.353
Maybe I just love too much,
okay?

02:24.353 --> 02:25.563
Well, where is
he supposed to be?

02:25.563 --> 02:26.772
[Spoon] He's supposed to be,
like, here.

02:26.772 --> 02:28.190
- Mickey!
- Mickey!

02:28.190 --> 02:30.401
Mickey!
What the hell?

02:30.401 --> 02:31.694
[beeping]

02:31.694 --> 02:33.237
