with the restaurant.

04:03.202 --> 04:04.495
Yeah.

04:04.495 --> 04:06.246
Or she's avoiding my dad.

04:06.246 --> 04:09.249
[tense music]

04:09.249 --> 04:10.876
♪ ♪

04:10.876 --> 04:15.506
