04:16.757 --> 04:19.343
Hey, what were
you and my dad talking about

04:19.343 --> 04:21.303
at the memorial service?

04:21.303 --> 04:25.808
Just that we both knew Dylan

04:25.808 --> 04:28.727
and how sad it was that he...

04:28.727 --> 04:31.021
Hey, Shira...

04:31.021 --> 04:32.231
♪ ♪

04:32.231 --> 04:36.777
Stay away from my dad
and my family.

04:36.777 --> 04:43.200
♪ ♪

04:44.326 --> 04:45.744
[sighs]

04:45.744 --> 04:47.371
♪ ♪

04:47.371 --> 04:49.206
[quietly] Oh, fuck.

04:49.206 --> 04:52.751
