09:51.967 --> 09:53.010
[sighs]

09:53.010 --> 09:54.177
[Spoon]
Okay. And she's gone.

09:55.262 --> 09:56.555
Oh, sorry.

09:56.555 --> 09:58.890
Wait, is that a tombstone?

09:58.890 --> 10:01.893
[machines beeping]

10:07.983 --> 10:09.192
Can I get you anything?

10:12.988 --> 10:14.865
It's just, um...

10:18.702 --> 10:20.329
I should have been there.

10:23.123 --> 10:26.335
But I was too busy
dealing with my own shit.

10:27.711 --> 10:30.380
I didn't protect him.

10:31.840 --> 10:34.426
Maybe my mom's right.

10:34.426 --> 10:39.222
Maybe I don't have any
maternal instincts.

10:39.222 --> 10:40.182
[chuckles]

10:42.142 --> 10:43.894
I meant like coffee.

10:46.271 --> 10:48.732
[dramatic music]

10:48.732 --> 10:50.901
[laughs] Wow.

10:50.901 --> 10:54.029
So this is why I never
see you guys at lunch.

10:54.029 --> 10:55.447
[Ema] Yep.

10:55.447 --> 10:57.949
♪ ♪

10:57.949 --> 11:00.327
Hey, Rachel, remind me.

11:00.327 --> 11:03.205
You and Mickey staked out
that club, right?

11:03.205 --> 11:06.792
♪ ♪

11:06.792 --> 11:09.461
You know, I knew that Mickey
was gonna go back to that club.

11:09.461 --> 11:10.670
I should have stopped him.

11:10.670 --> 11:12.672
I'm sorry. You knew?

11:12.672 --> 11:13.924
