would have listened to her.

11:17.803 --> 11:19.805
Okay, well, you're the only one
who's been there.

11:19.805 --> 11:21.181
So can you tell us
what it's like?

11:21.181 --> 11:22.641
Well, I mean,
it looked like a club,

11:22.641 --> 11:24.434
