what it was.

11:24.434 --> 11:26.686
It just seemed like
there was something...

11:26.686 --> 11:30.065
something bad going on there,
like scary bad.

11:30.065 --> 11:31.858
Well, we have to go.

11:31.858 --> 11:33.860
I mean, if they're the ones
who did this to Mickey, then...

11:33.860 --> 11:34.986
And if they have Ashley.

11:34.986 --> 11:36.696
♪ ♪

11:36.696 --> 11:39.491
Okay, I got these blueprints
off the JON network.

11:39.491 --> 11:43.328
Okay, I'm pretty sure that this
door leads to the side alley.

11:43.328 --> 11:45.914
Okay, so this vent looks
like it drops down

11:45.914 --> 11:47.374
into this room here.

11:47.374 --> 11:51.336
So working backwards...

11:51.336 --> 11:53.588
