through this thing out here

11:53.588 --> 11:56.258
and crawl through
to let us in that door.

11:56.258 --> 11:57.300
Okay, I want to do that.

11:57.300 --> 11:58.385
That sounds like fun.

11:58.385 --> 11:59.469
Wait. Shit.

11:59.469 --> 12:01.012
I can't remember
if I'm claustrophobic.

12:01.012 --> 12:04.599
I...no, I'm...no, I'm not.

12:04.599 --> 12:06.143
I'm not claustro...
I'm not claustrophobic.

12:06.143 --> 12:08.228
Do you want me to shove you
in a locker so we can find out?

12:08.228 --> 12:10.188
How about I shove you
up my butt?

12:10.188 --> 12:12.190
[laughs] Okay.

12:12.190 --> 12:13.275
So we have the blueprints,

12:13.275 --> 12:14.860
