and I have a gun.

12:14.860 --> 12:16.486
Yeah. Honestly, that is...

12:16.486 --> 12:17.404
yeah, that's huge for us.

12:17.404 --> 12:18.321
Yeah.

12:18.321 --> 12:19.614
So we're gonna do this?

12:19.614 --> 12:21.450
We are gonna do this.

12:21.450 --> 12:23.201
All we need are clothes
we look super hot in

12:23.201 --> 12:24.786
