13:01.281 --> 13:02.449
We'll be there in an hour.

13:03.658 --> 13:04.701
You guys ready to do this?

13:04.701 --> 13:05.577
- [Rachel] Yeah.
- Yeah.

13:05.577 --> 13:06.453
Yeah! Hell yeah!

13:06.453 --> 13:07.704
Let's fucking do this.

13:07.704 --> 13:10.582
Yeah, let the criminal
ass-kicking commence.

13:10.582 --> 13:13.585
[tense music]

13:13.585 --> 13:14.711
♪ ♪

13:14.711 --> 13:16.546
[engine starting]

13:16.546 --> 13:23.553
♪ ♪

13:27.390 --> 13:30.393
[suspenseful music]

13:30.393 --> 13:32.062
♪ ♪

13:32.062 --> 13:35.065
[footsteps]

13:36.316 --> 13:38.318
[machines beeping]

13:38.318 --> 13:39.569
[door opening]

13:42.739 --> 13:43.907
[door closing]

13:45.659 --> 13:47.202
