15:41.608 --> 15:45.111
that we would always be
bonded.

15:45.111 --> 15:46.529
♪ ♪

15:46.529 --> 15:48.073
[Lizzy] Thank you, Brad.

15:48.073 --> 15:51.034
You are so young, yet already,

15:51.034 --> 15:54.537
you seem to understand
that personal sacrifice

15:54.537 --> 15:58.792
is necessary
to protect the vulnerable,

15:58.792 --> 16:00.126
like our Dylan.

16:00.126 --> 16:01.670
♪ ♪

16:01.670 --> 16:06.299
Abeona is calling you.

16:06.299 --> 16:10.553
You come to me
when you are ready.

16:10.553 --> 16:13.556
[somber music]

16:13.556 --> 16:15.225
♪ ♪

16:15.225 --> 16:18.353
