17:20.749 --> 17:22.459
I actually am claustrophobic.

17:22.459 --> 17:23.877
Isn't that funny?

17:23.877 --> 17:25.377
[sighs]

17:25.377 --> 17:27.297
[groaning]

17:27.297 --> 17:28.631
[suspenseful music]

17:28.631 --> 17:30.341
Okay, I'm at the three-way.

