18:25.605 --> 18:27.315
- [audio cutting out]
- [jumbled speech]

18:27.315 --> 18:28.441
Spoon.

18:28.441 --> 18:29.692
- [line clicks]
- [line beeping]

18:29.692 --> 18:33.655
Uh, maybe he just hit
