18:37.242 --> 18:38.952
[Spoon]
Bro, just get off of me, okay?

18:38.952 --> 18:40.578
I'm just trying to find
the bathroom.

18:40.578 --> 18:42.789
Ow, stop...no, just get...

18:42.789 --> 18:44.332
[bouncer] Pockets. Pockets.

18:45.750 --> 18:47.001
What else you got?

18:49.504 --> 18:51.089
Very good.

18:51.089 --> 18:52.507
Where you going?
Where you going?

18:52.507 --> 18:55.552
Stay put, or I'll rearrange
your pretty little teeth.

18:55.552 --> 18:57.011
Do you actually think
they're pretty?

18:57.011 --> 18:58.596
I get really self-conscious
