18:59.931 --> 19:01.391
Shut the fuck up.
Shut the fuck up.

19:01.391 --> 19:02.892
Face the wall, and don't move.

19:04.477 --> 19:05.687
That wall?

19:05.687 --> 19:07.564
- Fucking idiot.
- I'm...I can do that, sure.

19:10.275 --> 19:11.442
What the hell is this?

19:11.442 --> 19:12.861
This kid just babbles
like this, man.

19:12.861 --> 19:14.445
He won't say why he's here.

19:14.445 --> 19:15.446
I got his phone.

19:16.531 --> 19:17.407
[Buddy] Hand it over.

19:17.407 --> 19:20.034
[tense music]

19:20.034 --> 19:21.160
He's got to be connected

19:21.160 --> 19:22.745
to that kid we got rid of
last night.

19:22.745 --> 19:23.955
