19:23.955 --> 19:28.459
♪ ♪

19:28.459 --> 19:30.128
Don't turn around.

19:30.128 --> 19:31.129
You here about Ashley?

19:31.129 --> 19:32.338
I'm just...

19:32.338 --> 19:34.132
I'm just looking...

19:34.132 --> 19:35.508
wait, is she actually here?

19:35.508 --> 19:36.926
You're not with Mickey?

19:36.926 --> 19:37.969
I said don't turn.

19:37.969 --> 19:40.263
Sorry. Yeah.

19:40.263 --> 19:41.639
How do you know I know Mickey?

19:41.639 --> 19:44.642
A teenage boy sneaks in
the day after he's here?

19:44.642 --> 19:46.811
Of course you're with Mickey.

19:46.811 --> 19:48.479
Where is he?

19:48.479 --> 19:49.647
He's in the hospital.

19:49.647 --> 19:52.442
♪ ♪

19:52.442 --> 19:55.320
[Candy] I'm gonna try
to help you, okay?

19:55.320 --> 19:57.196
Do whatever it takes to get
answers out of him,

19:57.196 --> 19:59.532
just not here
like the other kid.

19:59.532 --> 20:01.659
[bouncer] Got it. Say no more.

20:01.659 --> 20:03.077
♪ ♪

20:03.077 --> 20:05.079
My friends are in
the back alley, okay?

20:05.079 --> 20:06.873
