20:06.873 --> 20:08.833
Okay.

20:08.833 --> 20:11.669
♪ ♪

20:11.669 --> 20:12.670
- Move.
- All right. Okay.

20:12.670 --> 20:13.504
I bruise easily.

20:13.504 --> 20:14.631
