20:27.310 --> 20:29.103
Whoa. Chill.

20:29.103 --> 20:30.355
I know Mickey and Ashley.

20:30.355 --> 20:31.522
You know Mickey?

20:31.522 --> 20:32.899
- Ashley's here?
- [Candy] Yeah.

20:32.899 --> 20:34.484
And the guys here,
they got your friend.

20:34.484 --> 20:35.526
- They have Spoon?
- How do we help him?

20:35.526 --> 20:36.611
[Candy] You can't.

20:36.611 --> 20:37.862
