20:52.835 --> 20:55.254
What the fuck is this place?

20:55.254 --> 20:56.172
Hell.

20:56.172 --> 20:57.674
[ominous music]

20:57.674 --> 20:59.509
This place is hell.

20:59.509 --> 21:01.886
How do we...
how do we get to the dungeon?

21:01.886 --> 21:03.680
You need Buddy's phone
so you can get the code.

21:03.680 --> 21:04.597
Buddy?

21:04.597 --> 21:05.723
[Candy] Yeah, Buddy.

21:05.723 --> 21:07.517
He's probably in
the VIP section.

21:07.517 --> 21:10.144
