21:40.008 --> 21:41.634
If you don't see him,
he's already gone

21:41.634 --> 21:43.970
downstairs
into the VIP section.

21:43.970 --> 21:46.139
That's gonna make this all
much harder.

21:46.139 --> 21:49.017
♪ ♪

21:49.017 --> 21:49.976
Head down.

21:49.976 --> 21:51.728
Act like you belong.

21:51.728 --> 21:56.024
♪ ♪

21:56.024 --> 21:58.317
There's a nasty-ass
bouncer there.

21:58.317 --> 21:59.527
