21:59.527 --> 22:00.611
unless Buddy gives him
the okay,

22:00.611 --> 22:02.405
which isn't likely.

22:02.405 --> 22:03.656
♪ ♪

22:03.656 --> 22:04.949
You ready?

22:06.034 --> 22:07.243
Yeah.

22:07.243 --> 22:10.246
[dramatic music]

22:10.246 --> 22:12.290
♪ ♪

22:13.708 --> 22:15.376
Mind me asking
where we're going?

22:16.085 --> 22:18.171
You'll find out soon enough,
sweet cheeks.

22:18.921 --> 22:20.381
First you compliment my teeth,

22:20.381 --> 22:22.258
now you're
complimenting my cheeks.

22:22.258 --> 22:24.093
What do you think
about my hair?

22:24.093 --> 22:25.178
Fucking sucks.

22:27.180 --> 22:30.183
[siren wailing]

22:31.225 --> 22:32.852
[Spoon] Whoa. What are you...

22:32.852 --> 22:36.064
[suspenseful music]

22:36.064 --> 22:38.149
[engine starting]

22:38.149 --> 22:43.237
♪ ♪

22:43.237 --> 22:44.864
Got your friends inside.

22:44.864 --> 22:46.491
Thank you, Candy.

22:46.491 --> 22:47.492
Thanks, Candy.

22:47.492 --> 22:48.534
Of course.

22:49.744 --> 22:51.079
Why do you look familiar?

22:51.079 --> 22:53.539
I don't know.
I just have one of those faces.

22:54.540 --> 22:55.875
Sorry, what are you doing here?

22:55.875 --> 22:57.668
This is not safe for you
at all.

22:57.668 --> 22:59.545
It's not safe for you either.

22:59.545 --> 23:01.464
That's why I'm gonna get you
out of here.

23:01.464 --> 23:05.384
♪ ♪

23:05.384 --> 23:07.303
- Hello.
- Excuse us.

23:07.303 --> 23:08.221
♪ ♪

23:08.221 --> 23:11.474
Me and my girlfriend here

23:11.474 --> 23:13.935
want some time
with some of your best girls.

23:13.935 --> 23:15.686
Yeah. Yeah, that's right.

23:15.686 --> 23:17.688
We're lesbians.

23:17.688 --> 23:19.398
♪ ♪

23:19.398 --> 23:21.359
I'm sorry.

23:21.359 --> 23:22.985
Do you know who the fuck I am?

23:22.985 --> 23:23.945
♪ ♪

23:23.945 --> 23:26.489
I'm Angelica Wyatt's daughter.

23:26.489 --> 23:28.407
Yeah, that Angelica Wyatt.

23:28.407 --> 23:31.119
And if that doesn't
make me a VIP,

23:31.119 --> 23:33.704
then what the fuck does?

23:33.704 --> 23:36.082
♪ ♪

23:36.082 --> 23:38.209
