23:39.669 --> 23:41.587
Let 'em in.

23:41.587 --> 23:42.588
After you.

23:42.588 --> 23:43.714
Thank you.

23:43.714 --> 23:44.715
Thank you.

23:44.715 --> 23:51.472
♪ ♪

23:51.472 --> 23:52.890
All right.

23:52.890 --> 23:55.726
Time to make it
fucking rain, y'all.

23:55.726 --> 23:57.103
♪ ♪

23:57.103 --> 23:59.689
[chuckles]
Looking good, ladies.

23:59.689 --> 24:06.696
♪ ♪

24:14.829 --> 24:16.330
