that dolphin movie.

24:39.061 --> 24:42.440
♪ ♪

24:42.440 --> 24:43.900
Yeah.

24:43.900 --> 24:46.068
Yeah, I am.

24:46.068 --> 24:47.653
You want to know a secret?

24:47.653 --> 24:49.697
