24:51.032 --> 24:52.116
[notification chimes]

24:52.116 --> 24:53.826
No shit.

24:53.826 --> 24:57.038
[both chuckling]

24:57.038 --> 25:03.586
♪ ♪

25:04.921 --> 25:07.340
Is your real name Candy, or...

25:09.258 --> 25:13.012
No, but just call me Candy.

25:13.012 --> 25:14.388
I don't mind.
I picked it.

25:14.388 --> 25:16.098
It's the one thing
I got a say in here.

25:19.477 --> 25:23.064
You know, I think
you're right, from earlier.

25:26.234 --> 25:28.736
I feel like
I've seen you before.

25:28.736 --> 25:30.613
