for you anyway.

26:00.643 --> 26:01.560
Oh?

26:01.560 --> 26:02.436
No, come on.

26:02.436 --> 26:03.980
We're the same age, aren't we?

26:05.523 --> 26:06.482
All right.

26:06.482 --> 26:08.901
Well, how old are you?

26:08.901 --> 26:10.945
36.

26:10.945 --> 26:12.989
Oh, shit.

26:12.989 --> 26:14.657
I'm...yes. Okay, sorry.

26:14.657 --> 26:15.658
[both laughing]

26:15.658 --> 26:18.119
I'm...I'm 21, Spoon.

26:18.119 --> 26:19.996
Okay.

26:21.706 --> 26:22.873
Thank you.

26:22.873 --> 26:23.874
Yeah.

26:28.963 --> 26:30.506
Asbury Park.

26:30.506 --> 26:32.008
- You know Asbury?
- Yeah. Yeah.

26:32.008 --> 26:33.134
My grandparents have
a place there,

26:33.134 --> 26:34.427
and we would go
over the summers.

26:34.427 --> 26:36.637
