this striped sun hat.

26:45.062 --> 26:47.940
And I remember I wanted
that sun hat so badly.

26:47.940 --> 26:49.608
My mom.

26:50.943 --> 26:53.904
God, yeah, that was bef...

26:57.700 --> 26:58.868
