26:58.868 --> 27:01.829
[soft music]

27:01.829 --> 27:03.414
I'm 16.

27:03.414 --> 27:05.166
♪ ♪

27:05.166 --> 27:06.375
I'm 16.

27:06.375 --> 27:09.879
