27:09.879 --> 27:11.797
How did you end up here?

27:11.797 --> 27:13.466
I...

27:13.466 --> 27:16.802
♪ ♪

27:16.802 --> 27:18.387
Hey, look.

27:18.387 --> 27:20.431
We're gonna get you
out of that place, okay?

27:20.431 --> 27:22.183
Me and Ema and Rachel.

27:22.183 --> 27:24.101
