Let her go! Let her go!

34:08.005 --> 34:09.547
[Ema] All right, all right,
all right, all right.

34:09.547 --> 34:11.049
Don't hurt her.

34:11.049 --> 34:13.217
I'm sorry, that's not
how this is gonna work.

34:13.217 --> 34:15.053
Ashley, go. Get in the car.

34:15.053 --> 34:16.263
Your buyer is waiting.

34:16.263 --> 34:17.556
