34:30.944 --> 34:32.946
[groaning]

34:32.946 --> 34:35.072
♪ ♪

34:35.072 --> 34:36.199
Okay.

34:36.199 --> 34:37.784
Okay.

34:37.784 --> 34:39.828
Just stop.

34:39.828 --> 34:42.831
[engine revving]

34:42.831 --> 34:45.083
♪ ♪

34:45.083 --> 34:46.335
Stop.

34:46.335 --> 34:49.338
[engine revving]

34:49.338 --> 34:50.797
Ashley, stop!

34:50.797 --> 34:52.174
Ema, it's okay.

34:52.174 --> 34:53.967
No, we're not just
gonna let you go.

34:53.967 --> 34:55.302
