34:55.302 --> 34:57.429
Ashley, you want her to live
or not, huh?

34:58.722 --> 35:00.182
Huh?

35:00.182 --> 35:03.644
You want her to live or not?

35:03.644 --> 35:06.647
[engine revving]

35:06.647 --> 35:08.565
♪ ♪

35:08.565 --> 35:11.151
You mess this up for me,

35:11.151 --> 35:12.820
