your friend die.

35:12.820 --> 35:19.201
♪ ♪

35:19.201 --> 35:21.286
She's gonna kill me anyway,
Rachel.

35:21.286 --> 35:22.871
[gun clicks]

35:22.871 --> 35:24.373
♪ ♪

35:24.373 --> 35:26.750
Ema, no.

35:26.750 --> 35:28.669
No.

35:28.669 --> 35:30.629
Ema, no.

35:30.629 --> 35:33.173
Ashley.

35:33.173 --> 35:34.591
Wait.

35:34.591 --> 35:36.051
It's all right, Rachel.

35:36.051 --> 35:37.427
[Rachel] Just wait.

35:37.427 --> 35:39.513
[sobbing] Please stop.

35:39.513 --> 35:41.765
