35:41.765 --> 35:43.016
Stop.

35:43.016 --> 35:47.604
♪ ♪

35:47.604 --> 35:48.438
Sh...

35:50.274 --> 35:53.986
[dramatic music]

35:53.986 --> 35:56.113
[grunting]

35:56.113 --> 35:57.489
Ashley!

35:57.489 --> 35:59.366
Let go of her,
