35:59.366 --> 36:04.496
♪ ♪

36:04.496 --> 36:05.873
[Rachel] Ema! Ema!

36:05.873 --> 36:07.291
Are you okay?

36:07.291 --> 36:08.584
Mickey?

36:08.584 --> 36:10.252
♪ ♪

36:10.252 --> 36:12.129
Oh, Jesus Christ.

36:13.422 --> 36:14.464
Here.

36:22.306 --> 36:24.391
You guys gotta be
fucking kidding me.

36:24.391 --> 36:25.517
[Rachel] Mickey.

36:25.517 --> 36:26.977
- Hey.
- Hi, Mickey.

36:26.977 --> 36:28.186
Hey.

36:28.186 --> 36:30.439
How did you...
how did you find us?

36:30.439 --> 36:33.066
Spoon's stupid tracking app,
it goes both ways.

36:33.066 --> 36:34.318
Spoon?

36:34.318 --> 36:35.319
[door opening]

36:35.319 --> 36:36.445
[somber music]

36:36.445 --> 36:37.446
Spoon.

36:37.446 --> 36:38.447
Spoon!

36:38.447 --> 36:40.699
Hey, Spoon.

36:40.699 --> 36:42.034
Spoon.

36:42.034 --> 36:43.535
♪ ♪

36:43.535 --> 36:44.620
Hey.

36:45.996 --> 36:47.331
Are you okay?

36:47.331 --> 36:49.374
Are you...it's okay.

36:49.374 --> 36:50.792
It's all right.

36:50.792 --> 36:52.961
It's okay. It's okay.

36:52.961 --> 36:54.296
It's okay.

36:54.296 --> 36:56.214
♪ ♪

36:56.214 --> 36:57.215
What happened?

36:57.215 --> 36:58.508
- [person] Hey!
- It's okay.

36:58.508 --> 37:01.511
[ominous music]

37:01.511 --> 37:03.138
♪ ♪

37:03.138 --> 37:04.389
God, this fucking guy.

37:04.389 --> 37:05.891
