- What?

37:05.891 --> 37:07.392
He's on our side.

37:07.392 --> 37:10.562
He's Abeona,
like your dad, Mickey.

37:10.562 --> 37:11.605
♪ ♪

37:11.605 --> 37:13.899
Go here now.

37:13.899 --> 37:14.942
Go, go, go, go!

37:14.942 --> 37:17.527
All of you, go, go, go, go!

37:17.527 --> 37:20.530
[dramatic music]

37:20.530 --> 37:27.537
♪ ♪

37:41.093 --> 37:42.803
Dad, are you all right?

37:43.887 --> 37:45.263
All good.

37:45.973 --> 37:49.142
Look, I know
things aren't really great

37:49.142 --> 37:50.811
with you and Mom right now.

37:53.730 --> 37:55.273
She wants a divorce, son.

37:56.858 --> 37:59.528
Okay, so why does she want
a divorce?

37:59.528 --> 38:05.409
Everything's changed
since Shira came to town,

38:05.409 --> 38:07.703
your mom most especially.

38:07.703 --> 38:10.706
[soft music]

38:10.706 --> 38:15.293
♪ ♪

38:15.293 --> 38:16.962
Wait.

38:16.962 --> 38:18.755
Where you going? Troy!

38:18.755 --> 38:25.762
♪ ♪

38:36.857 --> 38:39.109
[sighs]

38:39.109 --> 38:40.736
Hey, are you okay?

38:40.736 --> 38:44.072
Um, no, no.
Everything is not okay.

38:44.072 --> 38:47.826
I just got texts
from Mickey's friends

38:47.826 --> 38:49.828
that they broke him
out of the hospital

38:49.828 --> 38:51.329
for a movie night.

38:51.329 --> 38:52.914
What?

38:52.914 --> 38:54.166
That sounds like a lie.

38:54.166 --> 38:55.333
You think?

38:58.295 --> 39:01.798
And also,
Troy came by here this morning.

39:01.798 --> 39:03.050
Troy came here?

39:03.050 --> 39:04.801
