I'm sneaking around with Ken

39:04.801 --> 39:08.680
and asked me to stay away
from his family.

39:08.680 --> 39:13.226
Okay, I am not
a home wrecker, Hannah.

39:13.226 --> 39:15.228
The only reason
I came back here

39:15.228 --> 39:17.898
was because it was
my little brother's dying wish

39:17.898 --> 39:21.276
for me to take care
of Mickey, my nephew.

39:21.276 --> 39:24.112
And now I am fucking
all of that up too.

39:24.112 --> 39:26.281
Shira, no.

39:26.281 --> 39:28.700
No, you're not.

39:28.700 --> 39:31.036
Please don't.

39:31.036 --> 39:34.081
Please don't go away again.

39:34.081 --> 39:36.625
