what that did to me.

39:36.625 --> 39:38.335
I can't go through that again.

39:38.335 --> 39:42.339
I'll tell Ken.
I'll do whatever you want.

39:42.339 --> 39:46.426
♪ ♪

39:46.426 --> 39:49.262
You're the only one
I've ever loved.

39:49.262 --> 39:56.269
♪ ♪

40:07.447 --> 40:09.032
- I have to go.
- But you just...

40:09.032 --> 40:10.408
I know, Mickey.

40:10.408 --> 40:12.285
♪ ♪

40:12.285 --> 40:14.037
Where?

40:14.037 --> 40:15.914
I don't know.

40:15.914 --> 40:17.499
