40:17.499 --> 40:24.506
♪ ♪

40:28.718 --> 40:30.387
I felt something
the moment we met.

40:30.387 --> 40:32.389
I...

40:32.389 --> 40:33.431
I can't explain it.

40:33.431 --> 40:34.474
Me too.

40:34.474 --> 40:36.643
Except, Mickey,

40:36.643 --> 40:38.562
that wasn't the first time
I saw you.

40:38.562 --> 40:40.105
What?

40:40.105 --> 40:43.775
