back to your camp.

40:52.284 --> 40:54.995
I saw you and your dad
together.

40:54.995 --> 40:57.372
He was comforting you
and telling you that...

40:57.372 --> 40:59.124
Doing the right thing
doesn't make you immune

40:59.124 --> 41:00.584
to all the bad things
in the world.

41:01.376 --> 41:02.794
Yes.

41:02.794 --> 41:04.504
Kylie's guys followed me,

41:04.504 --> 41:05.922
and then they caught me again.

41:05.922 --> 41:10.510
♪ ♪

41:10.510 --> 41:13.763
We were already connected.

41:13.763 --> 41:16.641
I think we always will be
in some ways.

41:16.641 --> 41:23.648
♪ ♪

41:25.150 --> 41:26.693
I wish you could stay.

41:26.693 --> 41:28.361
Me too.

41:28.361 --> 41:35.368
♪ ♪

