41:55.555 --> 41:56.598
It'll be a fresh start
and a better life.

41:56.598 --> 41:57.515
Where?

41:57.515 --> 41:58.683
Even I don't know that.

41:58.683 --> 42:00.143
Safer that way.
[whistling]

42:00.143 --> 42:01.061
Let's go. Let's go.

42:01.061 --> 42:02.520
Go, go, go, go.

42:02.520 --> 42:09.527
♪ ♪

42:09.527 --> 42:12.530
I'll always wonder
what could have been, Mickey.

42:12.530 --> 42:14.741
Me too.

42:14.741 --> 42:17.661
♪ ♪

42:17.661 --> 42:19.412
Maybe one day we'll find out.

42:19.412 --> 42:20.789
♪ ♪

42:20.789 --> 42:22.958
I really hope so.

42:22.958 --> 42:29.965
♪ ♪

42:43.103 --> 42:44.229
[door closes]

43:03.873 --> 43:06.167
