would have been extreme,

43:08.086 --> 43:10.255
even for me.

43:10.255 --> 43:12.882
But it served its purpose.

43:12.882 --> 43:14.759
They all thought that
I was a psycho criminal.

43:14.759 --> 43:15.969
Well, you can say that again.

43:15.969 --> 43:17.095
[chuckles]

43:21.433 --> 43:22.475
What?

43:24.102 --> 43:25.812
Last time I saw you,
you were a baby.

43:26.688 --> 43:28.273
