had Mickey.

46:09.476 --> 46:12.187
"As important as the kids
we've helped have been,

46:12.187 --> 46:15.523
"no kid is more important
to us than Mickey.

46:15.523 --> 46:17.775
"Kitty and I want
to leave Abeona,

46:17.775 --> 46:19.694
"and that's why
I'm asking for your help,

46:19.694 --> 46:21.988
"because we both know
how hard it is to leave.

46:21.988 --> 46:24.032
"I hope Abeona accepts
our decision,

46:24.032 --> 46:26.826
