46:29.954 --> 46:31.206
You killed him!

46:31.206 --> 46:33.333
You didn't want him
to leave Abeona, huh?

46:33.333 --> 46:36.711
So you sent that paramedic
to kill him?

46:36.711 --> 46:39.172
That's why you knew
so much about me, huh?

46:39.172 --> 46:41.007
That's why you've been
in my fucking head,

46:41.007 --> 46:43.259
telling me my dad
is still alive, huh?

46:43.259 --> 46:46.346
[singer] ♪ Are all I know ♪

46:46.346 --> 46:49.349
