You know that's not true.

48:14.100 --> 48:15.685
- In your heart, you know...
- This whole time?

48:15.685 --> 48:17.312
...that I adored your father.

48:17.312 --> 48:18.563
But people die.

48:18.563 --> 48:21.774
♪ ♪

48:21.774 --> 48:24.652
And now you know
all about that as well.

48:24.652 --> 48:27.196
But look at you.

48:27.196 --> 48:29.490
You saved Ashley.

48:29.490 --> 48:32.660
You and your friends
rescued her.

48:32.660 --> 48:35.246
♪ ♪

48:35.246 --> 48:37.749
And you will rescue more.

48:37.749 --> 48:40.585
♪ ♪

48:40.585 --> 48:42.754
That is your legacy.

48:42.754 --> 48:44.213
Look around you.

48:44.213 --> 48:47.133
Look at all the faces
of those we've saved.

48:47.133 --> 48:53.806
Your father,
he also rescued children...

48:53.806 --> 48:57.226
♪ ♪

48:57.226 --> 48:59.270
...including Luther.

48:59.270 --> 49:04.567
♪ ♪

49:04.567 --> 49:05.943
That's his name?

49:05.943 --> 49:07.111
Yes.

49:27.882 --> 49:30.301
Dylan says he's my butcher.

49:31.594 --> 49:33.221
He...he is.

49:33.221 --> 49:36.015
But yet my father rescued him?

49:36.015 --> 49:37.642
That's what you just said.

49:37.642 --> 49:39.143
So explain that.

49:40.186 --> 49:44.816
It's...it's a terrible story.

49:44.816 --> 49:47.819
[ominous music]

49:47.819 --> 49:48.986
♪ ♪

49:48.986 --> 49:51.322
[Mickey] Tell me.

49:51.322 --> 49:53.157
